Name: UCSB
Description: A great University located along the California Coast!

Name: Mammoth Lakes
Description: Beautiful mountain, with small town and offers ski resorts and endless lakes for winter and summer activities.

Name: Manhattan Beach
Description: Beach town located in the south bay of Los Angeles. It has sunny weather and consistent waves for surfing.

Name: Leo Carrilo State Park
Description: Beach along the California coast just north of malibu. It has pretty caves and rock formations all along the shore.

Name: Portland
Description: Big city located in the Pacific NorthWest. The pace of the city is relatively slow for its size offering a nice calm living space.

Name: Santa Catalina Island
Description: Small Island roughly 25 miles from the coast of San Pedro. There is an abubdance of snorkeling and kelp forrest to explore.
